    "author_association": "NONE",
    "body": "In Bootstrap documentation and other similar plugins they say `collapse,` `collapsing`, `collapsed` and `collapsible`. http://getbootstrap.com/javascript/#collapse-example-accordion\n\nI think `collapse` is pretty good verb as it really shows what it is for compared to `hide`, `slide up`, `accordion` or something else.\n",
